# Ignore target directories (not needed in build context except for pre-built binaries)
**/target/debug
**/target/doc
**/target/.fingerprint
**/target/incremental
**/node_modules
**/.git
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log

# Ignore IDE/config files
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/CLAUDE.md

# Ignore Docker files (except docker-compose)
**/Dockerfile*
!**/docker-compose*
